The Feature Complete build is a major step forward from Closed Beta, containing a much larger pool of exciting rounds and a raft of new features. You can look forward to: 

 •16 unique rounds, curated by our ‘Director’ 
•Online Parties - go through a Show with up to 3 other players in your party!
 •Season rewards and a Store where you can purchase items with currency earned through competing,
•Loads of customization options!  

 Enjoy Fall Guys Feature Complete!
You’re about to star in the greatest gameshow ever created, so let’s take a quick look at how things will play out… and the prizes you can win!

Hit “Play” to enter into a Show. You’ll need to race, chase and outwit 59 other contestants across a random selection of Rounds until YOU are crowned the winner!\n\nGet eliminated? Try again - the cameras are always rolling!

Compete in Shows to earn Kudos and win them to collect Crowns - you can cash these in for cool prizes to dress up your Fall Guy. Plus, you can unlock special rewards every Season by playing and building up your Fame level!
As well as jumping, diving and grabbing you can move with {action=Move} and adjust the camera with {action=Camera}
That’s it - hit the “Play” button after this message to begin a Show. Go get those crowns!
